                    <td class="views-field views-field-title-1" > Programmer Analyst III </td>
                    <td class="views-field views-field-field-opening-positions" > 1 </td>
                    <td class="views-field views-field-body" ><p>Ref. #: 5619.007<br />
                        JOB LOCATION: Twinsburg, Ohio<br />
                        JOB DUTIES: ):  Design and develop product features and customer solutions.  Conduct technical expert calls and workshops in collaboration with business consultants or clients directly to understand their needs.  Develop and maintain lightweight documentation of results.  Develop and periodically review fit with target architecture.  Write code for products to address customer needs.  Work effectively individually and with team members toward customer satisfaction and success.  Create Proof of Concepts and be involved with Architecture Design.  Perform process gap analysis against critical requirements.  Travel and/or relocation to various unanticipated locations throughout the U.S. required.  Utilize the following tools and technologies:  Java, Javascript, PL/SQL, JSP, Servlets, Hibernate, Oracle, IBM DB2. </p>
                      <p>SPECIAL SKILLS:<br />
                        Position requires a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science or Engineering and five years progressively responsible experience. Two (2) years of the aforementioned five years of progressively responsible experience must have included: (1) Java, (2) Javascript, (3) PL/SQL, (4) JSP, (5) Servlets, (6) Hibernate, (7) Oracle, and (8) IBM DB2. Travel and/or relocation to various unanticipated locations throughout the U.S. required.</p>
